org.svvrl.goal.gui.undo

Class RemoveAccSetEdit

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.swing.undo.AbstractUndoableEdit
      • org.svvrl.goal.gui.undo.RemoveAccSetEdit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.undo.UndoableEdit

    public class RemoveAccSetEdit
extends javax.swing.undo.AbstractUndoableEdit
    This class provides an undoable edit for the removal of an acceptance set (or pair) in an acceptance condition.
    Author:
    Ming-Hsien Tsai
